"Test & en operaciones matriciales

"1. B^T * D * B con unidades

'Datos con unidades:
E_u = 200000 MPa
t_u = 0.2 m
L_u = 1 m

'D constitutiva (tiene E*t = MPa*m = kN/m):
D_u = E_u*t_u*[1; 0.2|0.2; 1]
D_u

'B deformacion (tiene 1/L = 1/m):
B_u = [1/L_u; 0; -1/L_u; 0|0; 1/L_u; 0; -1/L_u]
B_u

'Multiplicacion directa:
BtDB_u = transp(B_u)*D_u*B_u
BtDB_u

"2. Misma operacion con & al final
BtDB_a = transp(B_u)*D_u*B_u & [kN/m; kN/m; kN/m; kN/m|kN/m; kN/m; kN/m; kN/m|kN/m; kN/m; kN/m; kN/m|kN/m; kN/m; kN/m; kN/m]
BtDB_a

"3. Misma operacion adimensional (N y mm)
E_n = E_u & MPa
t_n = t_u & mm
L_n = L_u & mm
D_n = E_n*t_n*[1; 0.2|0.2; 1]
B_n = [1/L_n; 0; -1/L_n; 0|0; 1/L_n; 0; -1/L_n]
BtDB_n = transp(B_n)*D_n*B_n
BtDB_n

"4. Sistema K*u = F con & en clsolve
K_u = [200 kN/m; -100 kN/m|-100 kN/m; 300 kN/m]
F_u = [10 kN; -5 kN]
'Con & en clsolve:
u_a = clsolve(K_u; F_u) & [mm; mm]
u_a
'Sin & (directo):
u_d = clsolve(K_u; F_u)
u_d
